        </div>

        <div class="research-item">
            <h3>Pregnancy Outcomes and CVD Risk</h3>
            <p>Research establishing pregnancy complications as independent predictors of future cardiovascular disease.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="research-item">
            <h3>Women in Interventional Cardiology</h3>
            <p>Studies on outcomes of interventional procedures in women and sex-specific considerations in treatment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="research-item">
            <h3>Contrast-Induced Nephropathy</h3>
            <p>Pioneering work on preventing kidney injury from contrast dye used in cardiac catheterization.</p>
        </div>
